{"tid":572244,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［大怒］啱啱同屋企人去廟街測字，個睇相佬戇鳩鳩","createTime":"2018-02-25T11:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T12:02:13.000Z","uid":5077,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00a0cbb16950d47fe62efca3b49da161ca34ba6d","tid":572244,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"啱啱同親戚食完飯，喺廟街行返轉，<br />\n經過檔嘢，有個風水佬叫晒我地過去，<br />\n話嚟測字，唔準唔收錢，<br />\n<br />\n我地成班見無傷大雅咪玩吓囉，<br />\n一坐低佢就問我姓咩，我話姓葉，<br />\n佢就話我第時一定大富大貴，結埋婚就最好，<br />\n之後到呀爸同呀叔，佢又係咁樣講，<br />\n我地就覺得奇怪，佢講嚟講去都係嗰幾句，<br />\n咁就問佢點解會咁講，<br />\n<br />\n佢就答：「姓葉者，年時非富則貴，婚者更甚。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為葉山豪，葉先生好豪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2683c7fe96f7b90863ccc3a49730fc339c7bf584","tid":572244,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"鴻福郎分身ac?"},{"pid":"0dd7f3318eb402a9f79b3437135434f1e319e8b0","tid":572244,"uid":90605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"ad7c59413345cc170606deee1feee9f8aac7efd5","tid":572244,"uid":35572,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/25/200051_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F25%2F200051_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=387e6823&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"029ce5f820b1318a76b2d3c49b9253a023776deb","tid":572244,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"啱啱同屋企人去廟街見到有人測字 仔友正一戇鳩仔"}]}